  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      ADHD children have executive function (EF) impairments,so we randomize the children to the
      training or a waitlist to improve EF ,adding contingent reinforcement to ascertain whether EF
      deficits are amenable to the training in children with ADHD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
